contentTypeXmls:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<type>
  <name>my_type</name>
  <module>mymodule</module>
  <display-name />
  <content-display-name-script />
  <super-type>system:unstructured</super-type>
  <is-abstract>false</is-abstract>
  <is-final>false</is-final>
  <allow-child-content>true</allow-child-content>
  <form>
    <input type="TextLine" name="inputText1">
      <label>Line Text 1</label>
      <immutable>false</immutable>
      <indexed>false</indexed>
      <custom-text />
      <help-text>Help text line 1</help-text>
      <occurrences minimum="1" maximum="1" />
    </input>
    <input type="TextLine" name="inputText2">
      <label>Line Text 2</label>
      <immutable>true</immutable>
      <indexed>false</indexed>
      <custom-text />
      <help-text>Help text line 2</help-text>
      <occurrences minimum="0" maximum="1" />
    </input>
    <input type="TextArea" name="textArea1">
      <label>Text Area</label>
      <immutable>false</immutable>
      <indexed>false</indexed>
      <custom-text />
      <help-text>Help text area</help-text>
      <occurrences minimum="1" maximum="1" />
    </input>
  </form>
</type>
